{"tid":366822,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"nodejs 整的網可唔可以就咁dom 上去做手機app","createTime":"2017-08-20T10:02:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-21T15:50:56.000Z","uid":65030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4331ad3f1e0591bb2087a614650437c75fc70635","tid":366822,"uid":65030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T10:02:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51618f499829c18bef67c0c33d392f261175592a","tid":366822,"uid":40684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T10:06:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9faf8f88789dea91b772c42041670bcc9e76e0e1","tid":366822,"uid":65030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T10:15:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n姐係可唔可以將寫完的網頁就咁轉做手機APP"},{"pid":"0eab876b710ec91bfeaee9a3eeab29ded15042ac","tid":366822,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T10:16:05.000Z","msg":"Web pages === Mobile Apps? <br />\n假膠?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e24c2c911c10511ca4f8158973ff26039557d5a4","tid":366822,"uid":65030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T10:20:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Web pages === Mobile Apps? <br />\n假膠?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真心, 姐係唔得?"},{"pid":"5fbc2cc545f95277c74068ce28b44559a080f05d","tid":366822,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T10:47:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Web pages === Mobile Apps? <br />\n假膠?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真心, 姐係唔得?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你好似係問緊native mobile apps喎! 就咁dom上去就run到嘅, common sense話我知:<br />\niOS apps : Objective-C / Swift<br />\nAndroid apps: Java / Kotlin<br />\n<br />\n...... 咁囉! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c63cd38e60bbe57dfcec249261210d485a32d8d5","tid":366822,"uid":85524,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T10:53:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nnodejs寫backend<br />\n你要一寫mobile同web<br />\n<br />\n要react native(好似係)"},{"pid":"0853faf81a20e27df6ed76ec8972fa36bd9b6a59","tid":366822,"uid":65030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T11:14:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nnodejs寫backend<br />\n你要一寫mobile同web<br />\n<br />\n要react native(好似係)</blockquote><br />\n姐係普通website唔可以就咁轉做APP?"},{"pid":"56444bea31660705e37b505bfe96b88c788d233b","tid":366822,"uid":65030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T11:16:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nnodejs寫backend<br />\n你要一寫mobile同web<br />\n<br />\n要react native(好似係)</blockquote><br />\n姐係普通website唔可以就咁轉做APP?</blockquote><br />\nhtml+javascript(nodejs)"},{"pid":"d4cc52d6cebe7b15a1b3464b7e263eab1ce8f96f","tid":366822,"uid":85524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T11:22:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nnodejs寫backend<br />\n你要一寫mobile同web<br />\n<br />\n要react native(好似係)</blockquote><br />\n姐係普通website唔可以就咁轉做APP?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你要web定app?"},{"pid":"5cd1f8fd9e6b6db37360173877383e9f6d95f500","tid":366822,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T11:34:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nnodejs寫backend<br />\n你要一寫mobile同web<br />\n<br />\n要react native(好似係)</blockquote><br />\n姐係普通website唔可以就咁轉做APP?</blockquote><br />\nhtml+javascript(nodejs)</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢D可以用嚟整web/hybrid apps囉!<br />\nBTW, React Native係可以用嚟整cross-platform native apps, 但都要通過現成/自製嘅bridge components嚟run in iOS or Android, 唔係真接run的!<br />\n<br />\n又要我搵番先前整嘅一幅Common Full-Stack Development圖畀大家參考下喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.ibb.co/mpumj5/Common_Full_Stack_Development_Models.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.ibb.co%2Fmpumj5%2FCommon_Full_Stack_Development_Models.jpg&h=45f190cd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"85eec5fab5841c3d8a7aa8b6cd29ff8764dcd831","tid":366822,"uid":65030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T13:19:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nnodejs寫backend<br />\n你要一寫mobile同web<br />\n<br />\n要react native(好似係)</blockquote><br />\n姐係普通website唔可以就咁轉做APP?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你要web定app?</blockquote><br />\n連登個手機APP屬於邊一種"},{"pid":"eae87fe140cd31ae00e221bbb4bf7f3d8d9dedba","tid":366822,"uid":75692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T14:17:02.000Z","msg":"node: cannot<br />\nreact native: can"},{"pid":"2f30bf1ba86b51f25d920d68b260972ac0a4e888","tid":366822,"uid":67527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T08:55:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nnodejs寫backend<br />\n你要一寫mobile同web<br />\n<br />\n要react native(好似係)</blockquote><br />\n姐係普通website唔可以就咁轉做APP?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你要web定app?</blockquote><br />\n連登個手機APP屬於邊一種</blockquote><br />\n連登Android係native裡邊部分畫面用webview(好似係)"},{"pid":"dd99b2dab9036f873a3ac5c5766a2e2a494b6d81","tid":366822,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T10:09:42.000Z","msg":"樓主最近出Post問Nodejs嘢出得好密<br />\n其實你有冇Google過先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f65f9d6a61019435c3a0a1de2a8c5d25379160df","tid":366822,"uid":11001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T10:47:39.000Z","msg":"Dom碌鳩落街算吧啦你"},{"pid":"ec88cfa936dc79c5e484bd219d87e46501e3c241","tid":366822,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T11:54:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主最近出Post問Nodejs嘢出得好密<br />\n其實你有冇Google過先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢好勁喎, 對Node.js不甚了解, 都可以攞佢嚟玩住web scraping先, 服咗佢! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cd819aad854b105609656848dac3d0b4e05a050","tid":366822,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T12:07:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓主最近出Post問Nodejs嘢出得好密<br />\n其實你有冇Google過先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢好勁喎, 對Node.js不甚了解, 都可以攞佢嚟玩住web scraping先, 服咗佢! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我第2個個人Nodejs Project都係做Web scrapping<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過都係因為咁\u001c先\b越嚟越識玩"},{"pid":"812f2dc00b040e38eb8d0349056cf1b66e472dc6","tid":366822,"uid":106027,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T12:10:25.000Z","msg":"其實樓主分到frontend 同backend未？"},{"pid":"91df3adb804a2969e83cffe415f2df1bacdd9f80","tid":366822,"uid":69481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T12:42:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>樓主最近出Post問Nodejs嘢出得好密<br />\n其實你有冇Google過先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢好勁喎, 對Node.js不甚了解, 都可以攞佢嚟玩住web scraping先, 服咗佢! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我第2個個人Nodejs Project都係做Web scrapping<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過都係因為咁\u001c先\b越嚟越識玩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nme too，都係scrape 高登<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac053e2c46dd47d7e99fa6a3a387f0af0534d728","tid":366822,"uid":67527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T12:49:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓主最近出Post問Nodejs嘢出得好密<br />\n其實你有冇Google過先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢好勁喎, 對Node.js不甚了解, 都可以攞佢嚟玩住web scraping先, 服咗佢! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實真係幾勁，如果我對Node.js不甚了解去做，啲async應該會亂晒<br />\n<br />\n不過其實web scrapping用async容易嘅language真係幾著數，大部分時間都係等server唔係真係process緊啲嘢。"},{"pid":"af4779283d92830c44d075ab48a0660129be17e7","tid":366822,"uid":2771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T12:56:31.000Z","msg":"好似有adobe phonegap"},{"pid":"4e58e0d293fb0a03ae87f32aa3a6e2125813284e","tid":366822,"uid":80656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T13:58:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nnodejs寫backend<br />\n你要一寫mobile同web<br />\n<br />\n要react native(好似係)</blockquote><br />\n姐係普通website唔可以就咁轉做APP?</blockquote><br />\nhtml+javascript(nodejs)</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢D可以用嚟整web/hybrid apps囉!<br />\nBTW, React Native係可以用嚟整cross-platform native apps, 但都要通過現成/自製嘅bridge components嚟run in iOS or Android, 唔係真接run的!<br />\n<br />\n又要我搵番先前整嘅一幅Common Full-Stack Development圖畀大家參考下喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.ibb.co/mpumj5/Common_Full_Stack_Development_Models.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.ibb.co%2Fmpumj5%2FCommon_Full_Stack_Development_Models.jpg&h=45f190cd&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔知點解有種怪怪的感覺<br />\n我會咁分:<br />\nUnderlyingLanguage--JS------------ PHP<br />\nbackend------------------Node.js------ Laravel/CodeIgniter<br />\nfrontend------------------angularJS--- N/A<br />\n<br />\n唔知你對呢種分類方法有咩見解"},{"pid":"d1ea90d37487585f47db76a42659d20c85115b8e","tid":366822,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T14:32:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nnodejs寫backend<br />\n你要一寫mobile同web<br />\n<br />\n要react native(好似係)</blockquote><br />\n姐係普通website唔可以就咁轉做APP?</blockquote><br />\nhtml+javascript(nodejs)</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢D可以用嚟整web/hybrid apps囉!<br />\nBTW, React Native係可以用嚟整cross-platform native apps, 但都要通過現成/自製嘅bridge components嚟run in iOS or Android, 唔係真接run的!<br />\n<br />\n又要我搵番先前整嘅一幅Common Full-Stack Development圖畀大家參考下喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.ibb.co/mpumj5/Common_Full_Stack_Development_Models.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.ibb.co%2Fmpumj5%2FCommon_Full_Stack_Development_Models.jpg&h=45f190cd&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔知點解有種怪怪的感覺<br />\n我會咁分:<br />\nUnderlyingLanguage--JS------------ PHP<br />\nbackend------------------Node.js------ Laravel/CodeIgniter<br />\nfrontend------------------angularJS--- N/A<br />\n<br />\n唔知你對呢種分類方法有咩見解</blockquote><br />\n唔...你果種分法比較academic同formal, 我果種比較practical掛。<br />\nBTW, 在下係大概以client-side development libraries/frameworks作frontend; server-side supporting languages/tools作backend黎分, 係粗略左D, 不過算容易理解既。"},{"pid":"2a97679e40cd465d5e99bc7e3dbac711827df78a","tid":366822,"uid":80656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T14:49:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nnodejs寫backend<br />\n你要一寫mobile同web<br />\n<br />\n要react native(好似係)</blockquote><br />\n姐係普通website唔可以就咁轉做APP?</blockquote><br />\nhtml+javascript(nodejs)</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢D可以用嚟整web/hybrid apps囉!<br />\nBTW, React Native係可以用嚟整cross-platform native apps, 但都要通過現成/自製嘅bridge components嚟run in iOS or Android, 唔係真接run的!<br />\n<br />\n又要我搵番先前整嘅一幅Common Full-Stack Development圖畀大家參考下喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.ibb.co/mpumj5/Common_Full_Stack_Development_Models.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.ibb.co%2Fmpumj5%2FCommon_Full_Stack_Development_Models.jpg&h=45f190cd&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔知點解有種怪怪的感覺<br />\n我會咁分:<br />\nUnderlyingLanguage--JS------------ PHP<br />\nbackend------------------Node.js------ Laravel/CodeIgniter<br />\nfrontend------------------angularJS--- N/A<br />\n<br />\n唔知你對呢種分類方法有咩見解</blockquote><br />\n唔...你果種分法比較academic同formal, 我果種比較practical掛。<br />\nBTW, 在下係大概以client-side development libraries/frameworks作frontend; server-side supporting languages/tools作backend黎分, 係粗略左D, 不過算容易理解既。</blockquote><br />\n明曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}